<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Procedure for Applying for Approval to Organize/Bid for a Sport Event - Malaysia Pickleball Association</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">
  <%- include('../../partials/header') %>
  <%- include('../../partials/sidebar') %>
  <main class="md:ml-64 pt-20 p-4 pb-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-center text-gray-800">Procedure for Applying for Approval to Organize/Bid for a Sport Event</h1>
      
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded shadow mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-red-600 border-b-2 border-red-600 pb-2">Local Level</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">Any organization of sports competitions at the national, state, district, division, or any administrative area level under local authority involving the participation of local citizens or permanent residents.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-red-600 border-b-2 border-red-600 pb-2">International Level</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">Organization of sports competitions in Malaysia involving the participation of non-citizens representing a country or individually, excluding those residing and working or studying in any part of the Federation (Malaysia).</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-red-600 border-b-2 border-red-600 pb-2">Licensing</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">Any company registered under Act 777, the Companies Act 2016 (application by a company representative).</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-red-600 border-b-2 border-red-600 pb-2">Sports Body</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">A sports body registered with the Office of the Commissioner of Sports under the Sports Development Act 1997 (Act 576) (application by the secretary).</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-red-600 border-b-2 border-red-600 pb-2">Non-Sports Body</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">Any organization or association registered other than under:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
          <li>Act 777</li>
          <li>Act 576</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-2">Includes:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-6">
          <li>Federal/State Public Government Agencies / Local Authorities</li>
          <li>Non-Sports Bodies / NGOs</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-red-600 border-b-2 border-red-600 pb-2">Application Process</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">Applications can be made via the link: <a href="http://erosa.kbs.gov.my" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">http://erosa.kbs.gov.my</a></p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex justify-center">
          <img src="/images/pic1.png" alt="Application Process Infographic" class="infographic-image">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <%- include('../../partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>